      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Mesh independence study — pressure drop and wall shear stress",
      "description": "Three mesh refinement levels (coarse 1.2 M, medium 4.8 M, fine 18.1 M cells) were evaluated. GCI-based discretization error for pressure drop is 1.4% (fine-to-medium) confirming mesh-independent solution at medium density. Aleatory variability in inlet turbulence intensity (estimated ±15% across operating cycles) is noted in the report narrative but no formal UQ artifact was linked to this result.",
      "hasUncertaintyQuantification": "https://uofa.net/morrison/uq/uq-01-gci-pressure-drop"
    },
