      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "PIV velocity field comparison at mid-plane",
      "description": "Computational velocity magnitudes at 47 PIV measurement locations compared against particle image velocimetry data. Mean absolute error 4.3% across all operating points. Experimental scatter due to cycle-to-cycle flow variability and blood analog fluid property variation across batches introduces aleatory uncertainty; the validation report discusses this variability in prose but does not link a formal UQ characterization artifact to this result.",
      "hasUncertaintyQuantification": "https://uofa.net/morrison/uq/uq-02-piv-experimental-uncertainty"
