      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Wall shear stress distribution comparison — blade surfaces",
      "description": "Surface-averaged wall shear stress on leading and trailing blade edges compared against oil-film visualization and micro-PIV near-wall measurements. Qualitative agreement confirmed; quantitative comparison limited by measurement resolution. Aleatory variability in surface roughness across manufactured test articles is mentioned in the discussion section without a linked UQ artifact."
    },
    {
